        <mxCell id="tf_label" value="Terraform 1.9.8&#10;&#10;Source: golden-image-windows/*.tf&#10;Backend: local (default for sandbox)&#10;&#10;★ Manages ALL hub-account resources:&#10;  • aws_imagebuilder_*  (pipeline, recipe, components)&#10;  • aws_iam_*  (roles, profiles, OIDC)&#10;  • aws_lambda_function + aws_cloudwatch_event_rule&#10;  • aws_ssm_parameter  (with ignore_changes)&#10;  • aws_s3_bucket  (logging, lifecycle, policy)&#10;  • aws_kms_key  (NOT — created outside TF)&#10;&#10;Run by: golden-image-terraform.yml"
                style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#00A300;dashed=0;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;"
