        <mxCell id="lambda_label" value="Lambda: golden-win2022-update-ssm-param&#10;Python 3.12 | 30s timeout&#10;Env: SSM_PARAMETER_NAME, SNS_TOPIC_ARN&#10;&#10;Internal flow on AVAILABLE event:&#10;  ┌─①─ imagebuilder:GetImage───────────────┐&#10;  │  (from event.detail.imageBuildVersionArn) │&#10;  ├─②─ Extract: image.outputResources.amis[0].image&#10;  ├─③─ ssm:PutParameter  → /golden-images/.../latest-ami-id&#10;  ├─④─ sns:Publish  → notify team/Slack&#10;  └─⑤─ Return success─────┘&#10;&#10;IAM permissions: SSM, imagebuilder, SNS, CloudWatch Logs (least-priv)"
                style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#7155ED;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;"
